1204
01:24:21,840 --> 01:24:22,160
Fantastično.

1205
01:24:22,320 --> 01:24:23,440
Odakle je došla ta naziv?

1206
01:24:23,600 --> 01:24:24,240
Flexibits?

1207
01:24:24,400 --> 01:24:25,760
